OL,3,CInside Cardiff's new bus station as it
OL,4,Copens after seven-year delay
OL,6,FCardiff's new bus station is set to
OL,7,Fofficially open this weekend after a
OL,8,Fseven-year delay.
OL,10,FThe Welsh capital has been without an
OL,11,Fofficial bus station since the former
OL,12,Fone was demolished in 2015, as part of
OL,13,Fthe Central Square redevelopment plans.
OL,15,FOfficially named Cardiff Bus
OL,16,FInterchange, it's located next to
OL,17,FCardiff Central railway station in the
OL,18,Fcity centre, and will open for bus
OL,19,Fservices on Sunday, 30 June.
