OL,3,CInside Cardiff's new bus station as it
OL,4,Copens after seven-year delay
OL,6,FIt had originally been planned to open
OL,7,Fin 2017, but after setbacks, a new
OL,8,Fplan was approved in 2018, followed by
OL,9,Fdelays and the Covid pandemic.
OL,11,FCardiff Bus say a "proportion" of its
OL,12,Fservices will now start and end there.
OL,14,FCoaches will not be running from the
OL,15,Fbus station, but TfW said it is
OL,16,Fexploring how this service can be
OL,17,Fdelivered in the future.
