OL,3,CInside Cardiff's new bus station as it
OL,4,Copens after seven-year delay
OL,6,FMarie Daly, chief customer and culture
OL,7,Fofficer at Transport for Wales, said
OL,8,Fthe team are "very, very excited and
OL,9,Fproud.
OL,11,F"We'll see our first service operate
OL,12,Ffrom here at 7:10am on Sunday, 30
OL,13,FJune, and we're just all really proud
OL,14,Fto see that moment happen.
OL,16,F"We'll have customer ambassadors that
OL,17,Fwork across both and offer a seamless
OL,18,Fservice for our customers from rail to
OL,19,Fbus and bus to rail.
