OL,6,F"There are customer information
OL,7,Fscreens that are around the building -
OL,8,Fthey will have the bus information and
OL,9,Ftimetable, and they'll also have the
OL,10,Frail information and timetable which
OL,11,Fcreates that connectivity between the
OL,12,Ftwo modes of travel."
OL,14,FMs Daly explained how TfW has worked
OL,15,Fto try and make the interchange more
OL,16,Faccessible.
