OL,3,CInside Cardiff's new bus station as it
OL,4,Copens after seven-year delay
OL,6,F"This facility offers that greater
OL,7,Fconnectivity with rail and bus so from
OL,8,Fa customer's point-to-point journey,
OL,9,Fwe're able to offer a more integrated
OL,10,Fand seamless service, and also this
OL,11,Ffacility offers a wider opportunity
OL,12,Ffor accessibility customers to be able
OL,13,Fto use transport and that's been
OL,14,Freally important to us as part of the
OL,15,Fbuild and design.
