OL,3,CInside Cardiff's new bus station as it
OL,4,Copens after seven-year delay
OL,6,F"What we've been looking at as well is
OL,7,Fabout how we share information about
OL,8,Fonward journeys and where people need
OL,9,Fto catch buses, so it is about trying
OL,10,Fto make that journey as seamless as
OL,11,Fpossible and accepting that we can't
OL,12,Fget all the services that we would
OL,13,Fpotentially like to have operate
OL,14,Foutside of the station, but we are
OL,15,Freally focused on making sure that
OL,16,Fwe've got that integrated approach to
OL,17,Ftransport."
