OL,3,CInside Cardiff's new bus station as it
OL,4,Copens after seven-year delay
OL,6,FCraig Hampton-Stone, managing director
OL,7,Fof Cardiff Bus, said: "This provides
OL,8,Fthe new focal point for our services
OL,9,Fthat start from the city centre. We
OL,10,Fhave a proportion of our services that
OL,11,Fwill start and finish here now (in
OL,12,FCardiff)."
OL,14,FThe multi-million pound facility has
OL,15,F14 bus bays, with more planned for the
OL,16,Fsouth in the future.
OL,18,F"We'll be taking a phased approach to
OL,19,Four use of this facility," said Mr
OL,20,FHampton-Stone.
