OL,3,CInside Cardiff's new bus station as it
OL,4,Copens after seven-year delay
OL,6,F"We'll be bringing a number of
OL,7,Ffacilities in when it opens on the 30
OL,8,FJune, and then we'll continue to bring
OL,9,Fthem in just to manage what the
OL,10,Fchanges might be to the customers so
OL,11,Fthey can get used to coming to this
OL,12,Ffacility in the first place.
OL,14,F"We will always have the same services
OL,15,Fthat will be departing and finishing
OL,16,Fat the same stands, we will always aim
OL,17,Fto provide as much consistency as we
OL,18,Fcan for the customers."
